{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Layout", "original_component": "BlueprintJS Navbar (48px height)", "patternfly_equivalent": "Masthead", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly Masthead provides same top-level navigation. Use MastheadMain for logo, MastheadContent for nav items, MastheadToggle for mode toggle. Height configurable via --pf-v6-c-masthead--Height.", "source_section": "Section 5.1-5.2"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Layout", "original_component": "Islands UI Pattern (modular panels)", "patternfly_equivalent": "Page + PageSection + PageSidebar", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly Page component provides Islands UI layout. Use PageSidebar for Fleet Island (160px), PageSection for content areas. Apply custom bg colors via design tokens.", "source_section": "Section 5.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Layout", "original_component": "Fleet Island (Sidebar 160px)", "patternfly_equivalent": "PageSidebar + Nav", "adaptation_notes": "Use PageSidebar with Nav component. NavList for train groups, NavItem for individual trains. Custom status indicators via Label component. Width: 160px fixed.", "source_section": "Section 5.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Layout", "original_component": "Status Island (Footer 28px)", "patternfly_equivalent": "PageSection variant=footer", "adaptation_notes": "Use PageSection with minimal padding for status bar. Contains zoom level, LOD view name, visible task count, fleet count. Text tokens: --pf-t--global--text--color--subtle.", "source_section": "Section 5.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Navigation", "original_component": "Navbar transparent tabs", "patternfly_equivalent": "Tabs variant=borderBottom", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly Tabs with borderBottom variant for Planning/Resources/Reports. Active tab uses --pf-t--global--border--color--brand--default.", "source_section": "Section 5.2"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Mode Toggle", "original_component": "LIVE/SANDBOX Toggle (custom)", "patternfly_equivalent": "ToggleGroup", "adaptation_notes": "Use ToggleGroup with two ToggleGroupItem. LIVE = default state, SANDBOX = active with violet accent. Custom colors: sandbox-accent #8B5CF6, sandbox-bg #0F0A1A, sandbox-border #6D28D9.", "source_section": "Section 7.2-7.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Search Input", "original_component": "Fleet Search (transparent)", "patternfly_equivalent": "SearchInput", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly SearchInput with custom styling. Set background transparent, border subtle. Placeholder: 'Search trains...'", "source_section": "Section 5.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Collapsible Groups", "original_component": "Fleet train groups (Alstom/Kinki)", "patternfly_equivalent": "ExpandableSection or Accordion", "adaptation_notes": "Use ExpandableSection for train groups. Header shows manufacturer + count. Collapsed by default for large lists. Alternative: Nav with expandable sections.", "source_section": "Section 5.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Status Indicators", "original_component": "Train status dots (в—Ҹ/в—җ/в—Ӣ)", "patternfly_equivalent": "Label or custom Icon", "adaptation_notes": "Use Label component with isCompact for status. в—Ҹ operational = success, в—җ maintenance = warning, в—Ӣ out-of-service = danger. Or custom SVG icons.", "source_section": "Section 5.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "KPI Display", "original_component": "KPICard with delta", "patternfly_equivalent": "Card + DescriptionList", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly Card with custom content. Title in DescriptionListTerm, value large text, delta with Icon (ArrowUpIcon/ArrowDownIcon). Status colors via --pf-t--global--color--status--*.", "source_section": "Section 8.2"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Alert Banner", "original_component": "AlertBanner (warning/danger/info)", "patternfly_equivalent": "Alert or AlertGroup", "adaptation_notes": "Use Alert component with variant (warning/danger/info). AlertGroup for multiple alerts. Use AlertActionCloseButton for dismiss. Custom action via AlertActionLink.", "source_section": "Section 8.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Button", "original_component": "BlueprintJS Button", "patternfly_equivalent": "Button", "adaptation_notes": "Direct mapping. Variants: primary, secondary, tertiary, link, danger. Use isSmall for compact areas. Icon support via icon prop.", "source_section": "Section 8"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Card", "original_component": "BlueprintJS Card", "patternfly_equivalent": "Card", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly Card with CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter. Apply custom bg-elevated (#1C1C1C) via CSS variable override. Border via --pf-t--global--border--color--default.", "source_section": "Section 8"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Tag/Label", "original_component": "BlueprintJS Tag", "patternfly_equivalent": "Label or Badge", "adaptation_notes": "Label for categorization (maintenance types), Badge for counts. Label supports colors via CSS variables. Use isCompact for dense areas.", "source_section": "Section 8"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Tooltip", "original_component": "BlueprintJS Tooltip", "patternfly_equivalent": "Tooltip", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly Tooltip wraps elements. 300ms delay recommended. Content via content prop. Position configurable.", "source_section": "Section 10.2"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Popover/Menu", "original_component": "Right-click context menu", "patternfly_equivalent": "Dropdown or Popover", "adaptation_notes": "Use Dropdown for menus with actions. DropdownItem for each option. Popover for richer content. Trigger via right-click event.", "source_section": "Section 10.2"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Dark Theme", "original_component": "bp5-dark class", "patternfly_equivalent": "pf-v6-theme-dark class", "adaptation_notes": "Apply pf-v6-theme-dark to root element. PatternFly 6 has built-in dark theme tokens. Custom overrides for bg-canvas (#0A0A0A), bg-panel (#141414), etc.", "source_section": "Section 4.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Semantic Zoom MACRO", "original_component": "Heatmap view (zoom < 0.5x)", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom (deck.gl/R3F)", "adaptation_notes": "No PatternFly equivalent. Use deck.gl HeatmapLayer or GridCellLayer. Cell = Month Г— Train. YellowвҶ’OrangeвҶ’Red gradient. Click to zoom.", "source_section": "Section 6.2"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Semantic Zoom MESO", "original_component": "Task blocks view (0.5x-2.0x)", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom (deck.gl/R3F)", "adaptation_notes": "No PatternFly equivalent. Use deck.gl ScatterplotLayer or SolidPolygonLayer. Block width = duration Г— pxPerDay. Colors by maintenance type.", "source_section": "Section 6.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Semantic Zoom MICRO", "original_component": "Detailed cards view (zoom > 2.0x)", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom (deck.gl/R3F)", "adaptation_notes": "No PatternFly equivalent. Use deck.gl TextLayer + IconLayer + PathLayer. Full task info: type, track, man-hours, duration. Dependencies as curved lines.", "source_section": "Section 6.4"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "LOD Transition", "original_component": "Opacity crossfade between LOD levels", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom animation", "adaptation_notes": "Implement crossfade at zoom thresholds (0.4-0.5, 1.8-2.0). Use Hermite smoothstep. Duration 200ms, easeOutExpo easing.", "source_section": "Section 6.5"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Sandbox Panel", "original_component": "Floating panel with changes list", "patternfly_equivalent": "Card or Drawer", "adaptation_notes": "Use PatternFly Card positioned absolute. Header: scenario name + controls. Body: KPI delta cards (3 cols), changes list with undo buttons. Footer: Discard/Compare/Apply buttons.", "source_section": "Section 7.4"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Compare View", "original_component": "Side-by-side baseline vs scenario", "patternfly_equivalent": "Grid + Card", "adaptation_notes": "Use PatternFly Grid with two columns (md={6}). Each column is a Card with canvas. Bottom row shows metrics comparison. Modal or full-page view.", "source_section": "Section 7.6"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Saved Scenarios List", "original_component": "Scenario cards with Load/Delete", "patternfly_equivalent": "DataList or Gallery", "adaptation_notes": "Use DataList for vertical list of scenarios. DataListItem contains name, date, change count, impact. Actions: Load, Delete buttons.", "source_section": "Section 7.7"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Minimap", "original_component": "120x60px viewport overview", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom component", "adaptation_notes": "No PatternFly equivalent. Custom canvas element showing heatmap overview. Viewport rectangle shows current view. Position: fixed bottom-right.", "source_section": "Section 8.4"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Color Tokens Background", "original_component": "bg-canvas #0A0A0A, bg-panel #141414, bg-elevated #1C1C1C", "patternfly_equivalent": "--pf-t--global--background--color--* overrides", "adaptation_notes": "Override PatternFly background tokens. --pf-t--global--background--color--primary--default for bg-canvas. Create custom CSS variables for MMS-specific values.", "source_section": "Section 4.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Color Tokens Maintenance", "original_component": "A-Check #10B981, B-Check #3B82F6, C-Check #F59E0B, D-Overhaul #EF4444", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom CSS variables", "adaptation_notes": "Create MMS-specific tokens: --mms-color-a-check, --mms-color-b-check, --mms-color-c-check, --mms-color-d-overhaul. Map to PatternFly status where appropriate.", "source_section": "Section 4.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Color Tokens Sandbox", "original_component": "sandbox-accent #8B5CF6, sandbox-bg #0F0A1A, sandbox-border #6D28D9", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom CSS variables", "adaptation_notes": "Create sandbox-specific tokens. Apply sandbox-bg to canvas when mode=sandbox. Violet border on navbar (2px top). Modified tasks get violet dashed border.", "source_section": "Section 4.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Typography", "original_component": "Inter font, 24/18/15/13/11px scale", "patternfly_equivalent": "PatternFly typography + Inter font", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly uses Red Hat fonts by default. Override --pf-t--global--font--family--sans to 'Inter, system-ui, sans-serif'. Scale similar to spec. Use JetBrains Mono for IDs/numbers.", "source_section": "Section 4.2"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Spacing", "original_component": "4px base unit (xs/sm/md/lg/xl/2xl)", "patternfly_equivalent": "--pf-t--global--spacer--* tokens", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly uses 4px base as well. Map: xs=4px, sm=8px, md=12px, lg=16px, xl=24px. Use PatternFly spacer tokens directly.", "source_section": "Section 4.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Border Radius", "original_component": "sm=4px, md=6px, lg=8px, full=9999px", "patternfly_equivalent": "--pf-t--global--border--radius--* tokens", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly has similar radius tokens. Override if needed. Islands UI uses subtle rounding - apply to Cards, Buttons, Panels.", "source_section": "Section 4.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Task Block States", "original_component": "Default, Hover, Selected, Conflict, Modified", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom CSS states on canvas elements", "adaptation_notes": "Not PatternFly - canvas rendered. Default: solid fill. Hover: brightness +15%. Selected: cyan border 2px. Conflict: red pulsing border. Modified (Sandbox): violet dashed border.", "source_section": "Section 8.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Empty State", "original_component": "Placeholder for no data", "patternfly_equivalent": "EmptyState", "adaptation_notes": "Use PatternFly EmptyState component. EmptyStateHeader with title, EmptyStateBody with description, EmptyStateActions with primary action button.", "source_section": "Section 15.7"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Loading State", "original_component": "Data loading indicator", "patternfly_equivalent": "Spinner or Skeleton", "adaptation_notes": "Use Spinner for loading overlays. Skeleton for loading placeholders in Cards/Lists. Bullseye to center spinner.", "source_section": "Section 15.5"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "User Menu", "original_component": "Avatar + dropdown", "patternfly_equivalent": "Avatar + Dropdown", "adaptation_notes": "Use Avatar in Masthead. Dropdown on click with user options. DropdownItem for each action.", "source_section": "Section 5.2"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Fleet Data", "original_component": "128 trains (79 Alstom + 49 Kinki)", "patternfly_equivalent": "N/A - data structure", "adaptation_notes": "Data structure unchanged. Used in Nav/DataList components. Prefixes: ALT for Alstom, KNK for Kinki.", "source_section": "Section 9.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Maintenance Types", "original_component": "A-Check/B-Check/C-Check/D-Overhaul intervals", "patternfly_equivalent": "N/A - business logic", "adaptation_notes": "Business logic unchanged. Visual representation: color-coded Labels/Badges. A=green, B=blue, C=amber, D=red.", "source_section": "Section 9.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Task Entity", "original_component": "Task data structure", "patternfly_equivalent": "N/A - data structure", "adaptation_notes": "TypeScript interface unchanged. Rendered via deck.gl/R3F layers. hasConflict/isModified affect visual states.", "source_section": "Section 9.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Scenario Entity", "original_component": "Sandbox scenario data structure", "patternfly_equivalent": "N/A - data structure", "adaptation_notes": "TypeScript interface unchanged. changes array tracks modifications. metrics calculated from delta vs baseline.", "source_section": "Section 9.4"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Keyboard Shortcuts", "original_component": "+/-/0 zoom, arrows pan, Esc clear, Delete remove, Ctrl+Z undo, S toggle sandbox", "patternfly_equivalent": "Custom handlers", "adaptation_notes": "Implement via useHotkeys or direct event listeners. PatternFly has no shortcut system. Document shortcuts in help modal.", "source_section": "Section 10.3"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Gestures", "original_component": "@use-gesture for pan/zoom/pinch", "patternfly_equivalent": "N/A - use @use-gesture/react", "adaptation_notes": "No PatternFly equivalent. Use @use-gesture/react for canvas interactions. onDrag for pan, onWheel for zoom, onPinch for touch zoom.", "source_section": "Section 10.1"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Modal/Dialog", "original_component": "Compare View as modal", "patternfly_equivalent": "Modal", "adaptation_notes": "Use PatternFly Modal for full-screen compare view. Modal variant large. ModalHeader, ModalBody (contains comparison), ModalFooter.", "source_section": "Section 7.6"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Undo/Redo Stack", "original_component": "Sandbox change history", "patternfly_equivalent": "N/A - state management", "adaptation_notes": "Implement via @belt/tools state machine or Immer patches. UI: Undo button in SandboxPanel, Ctrl+Z shortcut.", "source_section": "Section 7.4"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Performance Target", "original_component": "60fps, <3s load, 15k+ tasks", "patternfly_equivalent": "N/A - implementation concern", "adaptation_notes": "PatternFly components lightweight. Critical path is canvas (deck.gl/R3F). Use viewport culling (RBush), LOD transitions, WebGL instancing.", "source_section": "Section 11"}
{"task_id": "SPEC-002", "concept": "Storybook Phases", "original_component": "4-phase progressive refinement", "patternfly_equivalent": "N/A - process", "adaptation_notes": "Maintain phased approach: 1) Wireframes, 2) Layout with PatternFly, 3) Interactive components, 4) Polish. Approval gates between phases.", "source_section": "Section 15"}

